<plot>A young woman steals her best friend in the world, a horse named Jake, to prevent him from being sold to slaughter. But after driving to a remote, abandoned ranch, mechanical failure traps the animal inside its trailer. For three blistering days under the New Mexico sun she will try in vain to free him until she faces the toughest decision of her life: put the animal out of his misery or hope for a miracle.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?189638</url></doc>
